    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Plese send the whole stacktrace to be sure of previous answers.</p>\n\n<p>People here are probably right, but it seems strange that an IDE doesn't tell you that the return type of <code>clientService.callService(url)</code> is incompatible with the type of your variable...</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 26137201,
      "reputation" : 178,
      "user_id" : 19827057,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/eAPUxDRv.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "mariya cherian",
