  "title" : "String cannot be cast to org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity",
  "body" : "<p>While using the following code, I'm getting a <code>ClassCastException: String\ncannot be cast to org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity</code>.</p>\n\n<pre><code>@Autowired\nprivate  ClientService clientService;\n\npublic void methodA() {\n    String url = ...\n    ResponseEntity&lt;String&gt; resEntity = clientService.callService(url);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
